<P>
Photo, Elias Ortiz, left, and Rafael Godinez show where Ortiz found newborn 
baby Thursday. "You don't expect a baby," said Ortiz, who saw something move 
next to tractor tire. BORIS YARO / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
</P>
