<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Paramount Sues Video Firms: Paramount Pictures said it has filed a lawsuit 
against Video Broadcasting Systems and several Midwestern video companies that 
have allegedly placed local advertising messages on home videotapes of 
Paramount movies after the videocassettes were acquired by local video 
retailers for sale or rental. The lawsuit was filed in U.S. District Court in 
Wichita, Kan. 
</P>
