</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
SUITS; ADVERTISING; VIDEO RECORDINGS; PARAMOUNT PICTURES; VIDEO BROADCASTING 
SYSTEMS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080489-0115 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 90803 </DOCID>
